To generate the allure report
=============================
1. Follow the steps in https://allurereport.org/docs/playwright/ -> https://allurereport.org/docs/v2/install/
2. Add the allure bin directory to the Path variable.
3. Run the command - npm install -g allure-commandline --save-dev
4. To generate the report - allure generate ./allure-results -o ./tests/allure-report
5. To clean the previous report - allure generate ./allure-results -o ./tests/allure-report --clean
6. To view the report - allure open ./tests/allure-report